    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Summarize meeting notes with Google Drive and Microsoft Teams hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nSummarize meeting notes with Google Drive and Microsoft Teams hands-free. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual invoices is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Recent from Google Drive → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Render as HTML → Post Digest to Microsoft Teams → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating invoices in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Groq API key; Microsoft OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "78dc22b9-60a5-45bb-eedd-f5742852eb04",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
